{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775864662976,"sessionID":"ses_286399e5dffeQ3s6GyQQxPFoND","part":{"id":"prt_d79c6a1dd001mUotmRZKItPEyA","messageID":"msg_d79c68080001PIYb6aw5DSTBH3","sessionID":"ses_286399e5dffeQ3s6GyQQxPFoND","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"toolu_tool-44d76bd75e494dd2a0e5ddf09f36eff5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube codebase","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project codebase to understand:\n1. Project structure - find all main directories and files\n2. The pkg/agentd module - what exists there currently\n3. Any existing controllers in the project\n4. The AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRD types in pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\n5. Any existing proposal.md examples in the project\n\nFocus on finding:\n- Directory structure under pkg/\n- Any existing controller implementations\n- CRD type definitions\n- Any existing proposals or design docs\n\nReturn a comprehensive summary of the codebase structure and the relevant files for implementing an idle cleanup controller for AgentRuntime resources.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_286395db1ffeIHfT9NmgZLAgNp (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nNow I have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Let me provide a full summary:\n\n---\n\n## Comprehensive Codebase Summary for AgentCube Project\n\n### 1. Project Structure Overview\n\nThe project is organized at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/` with the following main structure:\n\n```\nagentcube/\n├── cmd/\n│   └── picod/\n│       └── main.go              # Entry point for picod service\n├── pkg/\n│   ├── apis/runtime/v1alpha1/   # CRD type definitions\n│   ├── common/types/            # Shared types (SandboxInfo, etc.)\n│   ├── picod/                   # Pico daemon for authentication\n│   ├── router/                  # Session routing and proxy\n│   ├── store/                   # Redis/Valkey storage layer\n│   └── workloadmanager/         # Workload management service\n├── changes/                     # Change proposals (AR-001 through AR-018)\n│   └── AR-XXX/\n│       ├── proposal.md\n│       ├── design.md\n│       ├── spec.md\n│       └── tasks.md\n├── idle-cleanup/                # Idle cleanup design/spec\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n├── go.mod                       # Module: github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n└── proposal.md                  # AR-007 proposal (K8s Reconciler)\n```\n\n### 2. pkg/agentd Module Status\n\n**pkg/agentd does NOT currently exist** - No files found at `pkg/agentd/**/*`. This module needs to be created for the idle cleanup controller implementation.\n\n### 3. Existing Controllers in the Project\n\n**No traditional controller-runtime reconcilers exist yet.** The search found only:\n- `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/scheme` import in `groupversion_info.go`\n- Controller-gen marker in `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n\nHowever, there is a **GarbageCollector** in `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` that implements idle cleanup logic using a polling approach (not a reconciler pattern):\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `garbage_collector.go` | Polling-based GC with `runLoop()` using ticker |\n| `lifecycle.go` | `SandboxLifecycleManager` for delete/expired checks |\n| `k8s_client.go` | K8sClient with dynamic client for Sandbox/SandboxClaim GVR |\n\n### 4. CRD Type Definitions (pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1)\n\n#### AgentRuntime CRD (`agentruntime_types.go`)\n```go\ntype AgentRuntime struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta\n    metav1.ObjectMeta\n    Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec\n    Status AgentRuntimeStatus\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n    Ports []TargetPort\n    Template *SandboxTemplate\n    SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration  // default: 15m\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration  // default: 8h\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition\n}\n```\n\n#### CodeInterpreter CRD (`codeinterpreter_types.go`)\n```go\ntype CodeInterpreter struct {\n    Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec\n    Status CodeInterpreterStatus\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n    Ports []TargetPort\n    Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate\n    SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration\n    WarmPoolSize *int32\n    AuthMode AuthModeType  // enum: picod|none\n}\n```\n\n#### Shared Types (`shared_types.go`)\n- **ProtocolType**: Enum (HTTP, HTTPS)\n- **AuthModeType**: Enum (picod, none)\n- **TargetPort**: Port configuration struct\n- **Label Constants**: `LabelKeyOwnerRuntime`, `LabelKeySessionID`, `LabelKeySandboxType`\n- **Annotation Constants**: `AnnotationKeyLastActivity` = `\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity\"`\n- **Condition Constants**: `ConditionTypeReady`, `ConditionReasonIdleTimeout`, etc.\n- **Default Values**: `DefaultSessionTimeout = 15*time.Minute`, `DefaultMaxSessionDuration = 8*time.Hour`\n\n#### Scheme Registration (`groupversion_info.go`)\n```go\nGroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{\n    Group:   \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n    Version: \"v1alpha1\",\n}\nSchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\nAddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n```\n\n### 5. Proposal.md Examples\n\nMultiple proposals exist in `changes/` directory:\n\n| Location | Title |\n|----------|-------|\n| `changes/AR-001/proposal.md` | CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n| `changes/AR-003/proposal.md` | CRD 共享类型与常量 |\n| `changes/AR-005/proposal.md` | Sandbox 创建处理器 |\n| `proposal.md` (root) | AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器 |\n\n**Proposal Format Pattern**:\n- Purpose/概述 section\n- Scope (In/Out of Scope)\n- Impact Analysis (Dependencies, Consumers)\n- Alternatives Considered (with pros/cons table)\n- Risks and Mitigations\n- Implementation Notes\n- References\n\n### 6. Key Files for Idle Cleanup Controller Implementation\n\n#### Design/Spec Files:\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `/home/dsj/.../idle-cleanup/design.md` | Complete design for `pkg/agentd` reconciler |\n| `/home/dsj/.../idle-cleanup/spec.md` | Requirements and scenarios for idle cleanup |\n\n#### CRD Type Files:\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `/home/dsj/.../pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go` | AgentRuntime CRD |\n| `/home/dsj/.../pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` | CodeInterpreter CRD |\n| `/home/dsj/.../pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | Labels, annotations, constants |\n| `/home/dsj/.../pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go` | Scheme registration pattern |\n| `/home/dsj/.../pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | Kind constants |\n\n#### Workload Manager (for reference patterns):\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `/home/dsj/.../pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` | Existing GC implementation (polling) |\n| `/home/dsj/.../pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go` | Sandbox lifecycle management |\n| `/home/dsj/.../pkg/workloadmanager/defaults.go` | Constants: GVRs, timeouts, annotations |\n| `/home/dsj/.../pkg/workloadmanager/k8s_client.go` | K8s client patterns |\n| `/home/dsj/.../pkg/workloadmanager/store.go` | MemoryStore implementation |\n| `/home/dsj/.../pkg/workloadmanager/types.go` | Store interface, error types |\n\n#### Dependencies (from go.mod):\n```go\nmodule github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\ngo 1.25.7\n\nrequire (\n    k8s.io/api v0.31.0\n    k8s.io/apimachinery v0.31.0\n    k8s.io/client-go v0.31.0\n    sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.19.0\n)\n```\n\n### 7. Implementation Requirements for pkg/agentd\n\nBased on `idle-cleanup/design.md` and `idle-cleanup/spec.md`:\n\n1. **Create package `pkg/agentd`** with:\n   - `reconciler.go`: Reconciler struct with `client.Client` and `Scheme`\n   - Time threshold: `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`\n   - Annotation key: `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey` (note: design says `\"last-activity-time\"` but shared_types.go has `\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity\"`)\n\n2. **Create binary `cmd/agentd/main.go`**:\n   - Scheme registration with core + sandboxv1alpha1\n   - Manager options: disabled metrics, disabled health probe\n   - Controller registration via `SetupWithManager`\n   - Signal handler for graceful shutdown\n\n3. **Reconcile Algorithm**:\n   - Get Sandbox CR\n   - Parse `last-activity-time` annotation (RFC3339)\n   - Compute expiration: `lastActivity.Add(15min)`\n   - Delete if expired, or requeue until expiration\n\n### 8. GVR Definitions (from workloadmanager/defaults.go)\n```go\nSandboxGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n    Group:    \"agents.x-k8s.io\",\n    Version:  \"v1alpha1\",\n    Resource: \"sandboxes\",\n}\nSandboxClaimGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n    Group:    \"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\",\n    Version:  \"v1alpha1\",\n    Resource: \"sandboxclaims\",\n}\n```\n\n### 9. Common Types (pkg/common/types/sandbox.go)\n```go\ntype SandboxInfo struct {\n    Kind string\n    SessionID string\n    SandboxName string\n    CreatedAt time.Time\n    ExpiresAt time.Time\n    LastActivity time.Time\n    Status string\n    // ...\n}\n```\n\n---\n\nThis summary provides all the necessary context for implementing an idle cleanup controller for AgentRuntime resources in the `pkg/agentd` module, following the patterns established in the existing codebase and the design specifications.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_286395db1ffeIHfT9NmgZLAgNp","model":{"modelID":"glm-5","providerID":"bailian-coding-plan"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube codebase","time":{"start":1775864554060,"end":1775864662973}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775864663027,"sessionID":"ses_286399e5dffeQ3s6GyQQxPFoND","part":{"id":"prt_d79c84bbf0015pzmeUexcGL8De","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d79c68080001PIYb6aw5DSTBH3","sessionID":"ses_286399e5dffeQ3s6GyQQxPFoND","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":18673,"input":3286,"output":230,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":15157}},"cost":0}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775864665369,"sessionID":"ses_286399e5dffeQ3s6GyQQxPFoND","part":{"id":"prt_d79c85516001ggJO112uiwAdx3","messageID":"msg_d79c84c06001zsIes3A905TtBg","sessionID":"ses_286399e5dffeQ3s6GyQQxPFoND","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775864669012,"sessionID":"ses_286399e5dffeQ3s6GyQQxPFoND","part":{"id":"prt_d79c862ec001vXdxkVFnlqlrKD","messageID":"msg_d79c84c06001zsIes3A905TtBg","sessionID":"ses_286399e5dffeQ3s6GyQQxPFoND","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-8c97a7032d904c14aa67f9d7efae5264","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: \n5: | 属性 | 值 |\n6: |------|-----|\n7: | AR | AR-007 |\n8: | Module | pkg/workloadmanager |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | L |\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## 1. Purpose (目的)\n15: \n16: 实现一个 Kubernetes Reconciler 控制器，用于管理 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组下的自定义资源：\n17: \n18: - **AgentRuntime**: 管理 Agent 运行时实例的生命周期\n19: - **CodeInterpreter**: 管理代码解释器实例的生命周期\n20: \n21: 控制器将：\n22: 1. 监听 CRD 资源的创建、更新、删除事件\n23: 2. 根据 CR spec 协调实际状态向期望状态收敛\n24: 3. 管理底层 Pod、Service、ConfigMap 等工作负载资源\n25: 4. 更新 CR status 以反映当前状态\n26: \n27: ---\n28: \n29: ## 2. Scope (范围)\n30: \n31: ### 2.1 In Scope\n32: \n33: 1. **Controller 框架搭建**\n34:    - 使用 `controller-runtime` 框架 (sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime)\n35:    - 集成 client-go 生成的客户端代码\n36:    - 实现 Reconcile 循环\n37: \n38: 2. **AgentRuntime 控制器**\n39:    - 监听 AgentRuntime CR 的变更\n40:    - 创建/更新/删除关联的 Kubernetes 资源 (Pod, Service, ConfigMap, Secret)\n41:    - 状态同步：Phase, Conditions, PodStatus, Endpoint 等\n42:    - 支持多副本部署策略\n43: \n44: 3. **CodeInterpreter 控制器**\n45:    - 监听 CodeInterpreter CR 的变更\n46:    - 管理解释器容器的生命周期\n47:    - 状态同步：Phase, Conditions, ResourceUsage 等\n48: \n49: 4. **通用功能**\n50:    - Event 记录 (Normal/Warning)\n51:    - Finalizer 处理 (资源清理)\n52:    - OwnerReference 设置 (级联删除)\n53:    - 领导选举 (Leader Election) 支持多实例部署\n54: \n55: ### 2.2 Out of Scope\n56: \n57: - Webhook (Validating/Mutating) - 由独立 AR 处理\n58: - CRD 定义本身 - 假设已存在\n59: - 具体业务逻辑 (Agent 执行、解释器逻辑) - 由其他模块处理\n60: - 监控指标暴露 - 由独立 AR 处理\n61: \n62: ---\n63: \n64: ## 3. Impact Analysis (影响分析)\n65: \n66: ### 3.1 新增文件\n67: \n68: ```\n69: pkg/workloadmanager/\n70: ├── controller.go              # 控制器入口，注册 Manager\n71: ├── agentruntime_controller.go # AgentRuntime Reconciler 实现\n72: ├── codeinterpreter_controller.go # CodeInterpreter Reconciler 实现\n73: ├── reconciler.go              # 通用 Reconciler 辅助函数\n74: ├── status.go                  # 状态更新辅助函数\n75: ├── resource_builder.go        # Kubernetes 资源构建器\n76: ├── predicates.go              # Event 过滤谓词\n77: └── suite_test.go              # 控制器集成测试\n78: ```\n79: \n80: ### 3.2 依赖关系\n81: \n82: ```\n83: pkg/workloadmanager\n84:     ├── github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go (已生成)\n85:     ├── sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime (需引入)\n86:     ├── k8s.io/api\n87:     ├── k8s.io/apimachinery\n88:     └── k8s.io/client-go\n89: ```\n90: \n91: ### 3.3 与现有模块交互\n92: \n93: | 模块 | 交互方式 |\n94: |------|----------|\n95: | pkg/apis/runtime | 读取 CR 类型定义 |\n96: | client-go | 使用生成的 Clientset、Informer、Lister |\n97: | cmd/manager | 作为控制器入口点启动 |\n98: \n99: ### 3.4 风险与缓解\n100: \n101: | 风险 | 影响 | 缓解措施 |\n102: |------|------|----------|\n103: | 控制器重启导致短暂不可用 | Medium | 使用 Leader Election 确保单实例 |\n104: | CRD 版本兼容性 | Low | 使用 apiVersion 检查 + conversion webhook |\n105: | 大规模资源性能问题 | Medium | 使用 Informer 缓存 + WorkQueue 限流 |\n106: \n107: ---\n108: \n109: ## 4. Alternatives Considered (备选方案)\n110: \n111: ### 4.1 方案 A: controller-runtime (推荐)\n112: \n113: **实现方式**: 使用 sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime 框架\n114: \n115: **优点**:\n116: - Kubernetes 官方推荐方案\n117: - 内置 Informer、WorkQueue、Leader Election\n118: - 与 kubebuilder 生态兼容\n119: - 社区活跃，文档完善\n120: - 原生支持 webhook\n121: \n122: **缺点**:\n123: - 框架较重，学习曲线稍陡\n124: - 调试复杂度高\n125: \n126: ### 4.2 方案 B: client-go 原生实现\n127: \n128: **实现方式**: 使用 client-go 的 Informer + WorkQueue 手写控制器\n129: \n130: **优点**:\n131: - 完全控制实现细节\n132: - 无额外依赖\n133: - 更轻量\n134: \n135: **缺点**:\n136: - 需要手写大量样板代码\n137: - 需要自己实现 Leader Election\n138: - 维护成本高\n139: - 与社区最佳实践脱节\n140: \n141: ### 4.3 方案 C: KUDO\n142: \n143: **实现方式**: 使用 KUDO (Kubernetes Universal Declarative Operator)\n144: \n145: **优点**:\n146: - 声明式操作定义\n147: - 内置状态机\n148: \n149: **缺点**:\n150: - 项目已停止维护\n151: - 学习成本高\n152: - 不适合简单控制器\n153: \n154: ### 4.4 方案选择\n155: \n156: **选择方案 A (controller-runtime)**\n157: \n158: 理由:\n159: 1. 官方推荐，社区支持好\n160: 2. 与现有 client-go 生成的代码无缝集成\n161: 3. 为后续 webhook、monitor 集成铺路\n162: 4. 降低维护成本\n163: \n164: ---\n165: \n166: ## 5. 设计要点\n167: \n168: ### 5.1 Reconcile 循环伪代码\n169: \n170: ```go\n171: func (r *AgentRuntimeReconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error) {\n172:     // 1. 获取 CR\n173:     ar := &runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{}\n174:     if err := r.Client.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, ar); err != nil {\n175:         return ctrl.Result{}, client.IgnoreNotFound(err)\n176:     }\n177: \n178:     // 2. 检查 DeletionTimestamp (Finalizer 处理)\n179:     if !ar.DeletionTimestamp.IsZero() {\n180:         return r.handleDeletion(ctx, ar)\n181:     }\n182: \n183:     // 3. 确保 Finalizer 存在\n184:     if err := r.ensureFinalizer(ctx, ar); err != nil {\n185:         return ctrl.Result{}, err\n186:     }\n187: \n188:     // 4. 同步期望状态\n189:     result, err := r.sync(ctx, ar)\n190:     if err != nil {\n191:         return ctrl.Result{}, err\n192:     }\n193: \n194:     // 5. 更新 Status\n195:     if err := r.updateStatus(ctx, ar); err != nil {\n196:         return ctrl.Result{}, err\n197:     }\n198: \n199:     return result, nil\n200: }\n201: ```\n202: \n203: ### 5.2 状态机\n204: \n205: ```\n206: ┌─────────┐    Create    ┌─────────┐\n207: │  None   │ ──────────> │ Pending │\n208: └─────────┘             └────┬────┘\n209:                              │\n210:                         PodCreated\n211:                              │\n212:                              v\n213:                        ┌─────────┐\n214:                        │ Running │\n215:                        └────┬────┘\n216:                             │\n217:                     Failed/Succeeded\n218:                             │\n219:                             v\n220:                       ┌──────────┐\n221:                       │ Terminated│\n222:                       └──────────┘\n223: ```\n224: \n225: ---\n226: \n227: ## 6. 实施计划\n228: \n229: | 阶段 | 内容 | 预估工时 |\n230: |------|------|----------|\n231: | P1 | 搭建 controller-runtime 框架 | 2d |\n232: | P2 | 实现 AgentRuntime 控制器 | 3d |\n233: | P3 | 实现 CodeInterpreter 控制器 | 2d |\n234: | P4 | 单元测试 + 集成测试 | 2d |\n235: | P5 | Leader Election + 监控 | 1d |\n236: \n237: **总计**: ~10 人天\n238: \n239: ---\n240: \n241: ## 7. 参考文档\n242: \n243: - controller-runtime: https://pkg.go.dev/sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime\n244: - client-go 生成的代码: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n245: - Kubebuilder Book: https://book.kubebuilder.io/\n\n(End of file - total 245 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n\n## 概述\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| AR | AR-007 |\n| Module | pkg/workloadmanager |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | L |\n\n---\n\n## 1. Purpose (目的)\n\n实现一个 Kubernetes Reconciler 控制器，用于管理 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组下的自定义资源：\n\n- **AgentRuntime**: 管理 Agent 运行时实例的生命周期\n- **CodeInterpreter**: 管理代码解释器实例的生命周期\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775864669000,"end":1775864669010}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775864669016,"sessionID":"ses_286399e5dffeQ3s6GyQQxPFoND","part":{"id":"prt_d79c85cb3001SYFezAp4dumSjj","messageID":"msg_d79c84c06001zsIes3A905TtBg","sessionID":"ses_286399e5dffeQ3s6GyQQxPFoND","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-84b6eade4a4144809a0d54e01cfa2933","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/idle-cleanup/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/idle-cleanup/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Idle Cleanup — Design\n2: \n3: ## Module\n4: \n5: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (see root `go.mod` in sandbox-orchestration design).\n6: \n7: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd`\n8: \n9: ### Time threshold\n10: \n11: ```go\n12: var SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n13: ```\n14: \n15: Idle expiration: `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`; delete when `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`.\n16: \n17: ### Annotation key\n18: \n19: The reconciler uses the same key as workload manager pod annotation for idle timeout tracking on the **Sandbox** object:\n20: \n21: - Import: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager`\n22: - Key: `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey` = **`\"last-activity-time\"`**\n23: \n24: (Workload manager also sets `runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout` on Sandbox metadata for template-driven idle configuration; **agentd** only reads `last-activity-time`.)\n25: \n26: ### Reconciler\n27: \n28: ```go\n29: package agentd\n30: \n31: type Reconciler struct {\n32:     client.Client\n33:     Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n34: }\n35: \n36: func (r *Reconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error)\n37: ```\n38: \n39: **Algorithm (exact behavior):**\n40: \n41: 1. `sandbox := &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}`; `Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox)`.\n42: 2. If `errors.IsNotFound(err)` → `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`.\n43: 3. If other get error → return `ctrl.Result{}, err`.\n44: 4. `lastActivityStr, exists := sandbox.Annotations[workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey]`.\n45: 5. If `exists && lastActivityStr != \"\"`:\n46:    - `lastActivity, err := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)`\n47:    - If parse err → `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30 * time.Second}, err`\n48:    - `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`\n49:    - If `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`:\n50:      - `r.Delete(ctx, sandbox)`; if err and not `IsNotFound` → `return ctrl.Result{}, err`\n51:    - Else:\n52:      - `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil`\n53: 6. `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n54: \n55: ### SetupWithManager\n56: \n57: ```go\n58: func (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error {\n59:     return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n60:         For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n61:         Complete(r)\n62: }\n63: ```\n64: \n65: ## Binary `cmd/agentd/main.go`\n66: \n67: ### Scheme registration\n68: \n69: ```go\n70: var schemeBuilder = runtime.NewScheme()\n71: \n72: func init() {\n73:     utilruntime.Must(scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n74:     utilruntime.Must(sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n75: }\n76: ```\n77: \n78: ### Controller-runtime manager\n79: \n80: ```go\n81: mgr, err := ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{\n82:     Scheme:                 schemeBuilder,\n83:     Metrics:                metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"},\n84:     HealthProbeBindAddress:   \"0\",\n85: })\n86: ```\n87: \n88: ### Controller registration (duplicate of SetupWithManager pattern)\n89: \n90: ```go\n91: err = ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n92:     For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n93:     Complete(&agentd.Reconciler{\n94:         Client: mgr.GetClient(),\n95:         Scheme: mgr.GetScheme(),\n96:     })\n97: ```\n98: \n99: ### Run\n100: \n101: ```go\n102: mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler())\n103: ```\n104: \n105: ## Watched resources\n106: \n107: | API group | Version | Kind | Trigger |\n108: |-----------|---------|------|---------|\n109: | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `v1alpha1` | `Sandbox` | Default `For()` watch — creates, updates, deletes (per controller-runtime) |\n110: \n111: No explicit `Owns` or `Watches` — single primary resource `Sandbox`.\n112: \n113: ## Related workload-manager constants (context)\n114: \n115: From `pkg/workloadmanager` (not used by agentd reconcile logic but set when sandboxes are created):\n116: \n117: - `IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey = \"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\"` — duration string on Sandbox CR.\n118: - `LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"` — **read by agentd** for idle cleanup.\n119: \n120: ## Dependencies\n121: \n122: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors`\n123: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime`\n124: - `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1`\n125: - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime`\n126: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager` (annotation key only)\n\n(End of file - total 126 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Idle Cleanup — Design\n\n## Module\n\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (see root `go.mod` in sandbox-orchestration design).\n\n## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd`\n\n### Time threshold\n\n```go\nvar SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n```\n\nIdle expiration: `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`; delete when `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`.\n\n### Annotation key\n\nThe reconciler uses the same key as workload manager pod annotation for idle timeout tracking on the **Sandbox** object:\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/idle-cleanup/design.md","time":{"start":1775864668995,"end":1775864669014}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775864669019,"sessionID":"ses_286399e5dffeQ3s6GyQQxPFoND","part":{"id":"prt_d79c85fd0001PvMGKN5aNFZWq2","messageID":"msg_d79c84c06001zsIes3A905TtBg","sessionID":"ses_286399e5dffeQ3s6GyQQxPFoND","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-90ae49a78ca6499eb8b7f456c401d5af","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/idle-cleanup/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/idle-cleanup/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Idle Cleanup Specification\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: Run a controller that deletes `Sandbox` custom resources when an idle-timeout annotation indicates the sandbox has been inactive beyond a fixed grace period.\n5: \n6: ## Requirements\n7: \n8: ### Requirement: Reconciliation trigger\n9: The system SHALL register a controller-runtime reconciler for resource kind `Sandbox` API version `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`, using the manager’s API reader/writer client for get/delete operations.\n10: \n11: #### Scenario: Sandbox watch drives reconcile\n12: - **GIVEN** a `Sandbox` object is created or updated in the cluster\n13: - **WHEN** the manager is running\n14: - **THEN** the reconciler `Reconcile` function is invoked with the object’s namespace and name\n15: \n16: ### Requirement: Idle detection input\n17: The system SHALL read annotation key `last-activity-time` (constant `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey`) from the `Sandbox` metadata. When the annotation is missing or empty, the system SHALL take no delete action and SHALL return without requeue (unless other logic applies—none in this controller).\n18: \n19: #### Scenario: No annotation means no deletion\n20: - **GIVEN** a `Sandbox` without `last-activity-time`\n21: - **WHEN** reconciliation completes\n22: - **THEN** the sandbox is not deleted and result has zero `RequeueAfter`\n23: \n24: ### Requirement: Idle detection parsing\n25: When the annotation is non-empty, the system SHALL parse it with `time.RFC3339`. On parse error, the system SHALL return `RequeueAfter: 30 seconds` and the parse error.\n26: \n27: #### Scenario: Invalid timestamp requeues\n28: - **GIVEN** annotation value is not RFC3339\n29: - **WHEN** `time.Parse` fails\n30: - **THEN** reconcile returns `(Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}, err)`\n31: \n32: ### Requirement: Expiration threshold\n33: The system SHALL define `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`. The system SHALL compute `expirationTime = lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`. When `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`, the system SHALL delete the `Sandbox` resource.\n34: \n35: #### Scenario: Idle beyond 15 minutes triggers delete\n36: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` parses to a time more than 15 minutes in the past\n37: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n38: - **THEN** the controller calls delete on the `Sandbox` client object\n39: \n40: #### Scenario: Not yet expired requeues until expiration\n41: - **GIVEN** `last-activity-time` is recent enough that expiration is in the future\n42: - **WHEN** reconciliation runs\n43: - **THEN** the result is `RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)` and no delete occurs\n44: \n45: ### Requirement: Delete idempotency\n46: When delete returns `NotFound`, the system SHALL treat it as success and SHALL return empty result with nil error. Other delete errors SHALL be returned to trigger retry.\n47: \n48: #### Scenario: Already deleted sandbox\n49: - **GIVEN** the API server returns not found on delete\n50: - **WHEN** the reconciler handles the error\n51: - **THEN** reconcile returns `(ctrl.Result{}, nil)`\n52: \n53: ### Requirement: Get not found\n54: When get returns `NotFound`, the system SHALL return empty result and nil error.\n55: \n56: #### Scenario: Sandbox removed before reconcile\n57: - **GIVEN** the sandbox no longer exists\n58: - **WHEN** `Get` fails with not found\n59: - **THEN** reconcile returns without error\n60: \n61: ## Requirements (binary / operator)\n62: \n63: ### Requirement: Manager options\n64: The `agentd` binary SHALL construct controller-runtime `Manager` with scheme containing core Kubernetes types and `sandboxv1alpha1` from `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1`, SHALL disable metrics server (`BindAddress: \"0\"`), and SHALL disable health probe server (`HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\"`).\n65: \n66: #### Scenario: Signal-driven shutdown\n67: - **GIVEN** the process runs `mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler())`\n68: - **WHEN** SIGTERM/SIGINT is received\n69: - **THEN** the manager stops gracefully per controller-runtime defaults\n\n(End of file - total 69 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Idle Cleanup Specification\n\n## Purpose\nRun a controller that deletes `Sandbox` custom resources when an idle-timeout annotation indicates the sandbox has been inactive beyond a fixed grace period.\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Reconciliation trigger\nThe system SHALL register a controller-runtime reconciler for resource kind `Sandbox` API version `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`, using the manager’s API reader/writer client for get/delete operations.\n\n#### Scenario: Sandbox watch drives reconcile\n- **GIVEN** a `Sandbox` object is created or updated in the cluster\n- **WHEN** the manager is running\n- **THEN** the reconciler `Reconcile` function is invoked with the object’s namespace and name\n\n### Requirement: Idle detection input\nThe system SHALL read annotation key `last-activity-time` (constant `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey`) from the `Sandbox` metadata. When the annotation is missing or empty, the system SHALL take no delete action and SHALL return without requeue (unless other logic applies—none in this controller).\n\n#### Scenario: No annotation means no deletion\n- **GIVEN** a `Sandbox` without `last-activity-time`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/idle-cleanup/spec.md","time":{"start":1775864668999,"end":1775864669017}}}}
