{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775864735747,"sessionID":"ses_286399e5dffeQ3s6GyQQxPFoND","part":{"id":"prt_d79c967b4001XOJ0KTgddJ7B3J","messageID":"msg_d79c8875a001tMjofpRuuoBvGu","sessionID":"ses_286399e5dffeQ3s6GyQQxPFoND","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-e85e7fe108ab44f49099900b29eafe90","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-018/proposal.md","content":"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n\n## 概述\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| AR | AR-018 |\n| Module | pkg/agentd |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n\n---\n\n## 1. Purpose (目的)\n\n实现一个轻量级 Kubernetes 控制器，用于自动清理空闲超时的 `Sandbox` 自定义资源。\n\n**Current State**: 当前项目中，`pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` 实现了基于轮询的垃圾回收机制，通过定期扫描检查 Sandbox 的空闲状态。这种方式存在延迟较高、资源利用率不优的问题。\n\n**Target State**: 引入 `pkg/agentd` 模块，使用 controller-runtime 的 Reconciler 模式，基于事件驱动的空闲清理。控制器将：\n1. 监听 `Sandbox` CR 的创建/更新事件\n2. 读取 `last-activity-time` annotation 判断空闲状态\n3. 计算 15 分钟空闲阈值，到期自动删除资源\n4. 使用 RequeueAfter 实现精确的延迟删除调度\n\n---\n\n## 2. Scope (范围)\n\n### 2.1 In Scope\n\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` | Reconciler 实现，包含空闲检测与删除逻辑 |\n| `cmd/agentd/main.go` | 独立二进制入口，启动 controller-runtime manager |\n| Scheme 注册 | 注册 core Kubernetes types + `sandboxv1alpha1` |\n| 单元测试 | Reconciler 核心逻辑测试 |\n\n### Implementation Details\n\n**核心常量**:\n```go\nvar SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n```\n\n**Annotation Key**: `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey` = `\"last-activity-time\"`\n\n**Reconcile 算法**:\n1. 获取 Sandbox CR\n2. 解析 `last-activity-time` annotation (RFC3339 格式)\n3. 计算 `expirationTime = lastActivity + 15min`\n4. 若 `now.After(expirationTime)` → 删除 Sandbox\n5. 否则 → `RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)`\n\n**Watch 资源**:\n| API group | Version | Kind |\n|-----------|---------|------|\n| `agents.x-k8s.io` | `v1alpha1` | `Sandbox` |\n\n### 2.2 Out of Scope\n\n- AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CR 控制器 (由 AR-007 处理)\n- Webhook (Validating/Mutating)\n- Metrics 暴露\n- 领导选举 (单实例部署)\n- 现有 `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` 的重构或移除\n\n---\n\n## 3. Impact Analysis (影响分析)\n\n### 3.1 新增文件\n\n```\npkg/agentd/\n└── reconciler.go           # Reconciler 结构体与 Reconcile 方法\n\ncmd/agentd/\n└── main.go                 # 独立二进制入口\n```\n\n### 3.2 Upstream Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Version | Impact |\n|------------|---------|--------|\n| `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` | v0.19.0 | 核心框架 |\n| `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1` | - | Sandbox CRD 类型 |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery` | v0.31.0 | API 错误处理、runtime.Scheme |\n| `k8s.io/client-go` | v0.31.0 | Kubernetes 客户端 |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager` | - | Annotation 常量 |\n\n### 3.3 Downstream Consumers\n\n| Consumer | Method Usage |\n|----------|--------------|\n| 运维部署 | 部署 `agentd` 作为独立 DaemonSet/Deployment |\n| Sandbox 资源管理 | 自动清理空闲资源，释放集群资源 |\n\n### 3.4 Breaking Change Considerations\n\n无破坏性变更。这是新增模块，不影响现有功能。\n\n### 3.5 Compatibility Notes\n\n- 与现有 `workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` 功能重叠，但互不干扰\n- `agentd` 可作为 garbage_collector 的补充或替代部署\n- Annotation key 需与 workloadmanager 保持一致 (`last-activity-time`)\n\n---\n\n## 4. Alternatives Considered (备选方案)\n\n### Alternative 1: controller-runtime Reconciler (推荐)\n\n**Approach**: 使用 sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime 的 Reconciler 模式，监听 Sandbox CR 变更。\n\n| Aspect | Evaluation |\n|--------|------------|\n| Pros | 事件驱动、精确调度 (RequeueAfter)、代码简洁、与 K8s 生态兼容 |\n| Cons | 需要独立进程运行、依赖 controller-runtime 框架 |\n\n**Implementation**:\n```go\nfunc (r *Reconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error) {\n    sandbox := &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}\n    if err := r.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox); err != nil {\n        return ctrl.Result{}, client.IgnoreNotFound(err)\n    }\n    \n    lastActivityStr := sandbox.Annotations[workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey]\n    if lastActivityStr == \"\" {\n        return ctrl.Result{}, nil\n    }\n    \n    lastActivity, err := time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)\n    if err != nil {\n        return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30 * time.Second}, err\n    }\n    \n    expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)\n    if time.Now().After(expirationTime) {\n        return ctrl.Result{}, client.IgnoreNotFound(r.Delete(ctx, sandbox))\n    }\n    \n    return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil\n}\n```\n\n### Alternative 2: 现有轮询式 GC\n\n**Approach**: 复用 `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` 的轮询模式。\n\n| Aspect | Evaluation |\n|--------|------------|\n| Pros | 无需新增进程、代码已存在 |\n| Cons | 延迟高 (轮询间隔)、资源浪费、无法精确调度 |\n\n**Decision**: 选择 **Alternative 1 (controller-runtime Reconciler)**\n\n理由:\n1. 精确调度：使用 `RequeueAfter` 在准确的过期时间触发删除\n2. 资源高效：事件驱动，无空转轮询\n3. 可扩展：未来可轻松添加更多控制器逻辑\n4. 与 AR-007 架构一致\n\n### Alternative 3: CronJob 定时任务\n\n**Approach**: 使用 Kubernetes CronJob 定期扫描删除空闲 Sandbox。\n\n| Aspect | Evaluation |\n|--------|------------|\n| Pros | 无需常驻进程、部署简单 |\n| Cons | 延迟高 (Cron 间隔)、无法精确调度、需额外 RBAC 配置 |\n\n---\n\n## 5. Risks\n\n| Risk | Mitigation |\n|------|------------|\n| 误删活跃 Sandbox | 解析失败时 Requeue 30s 重试，不直接删除 |\n| 时钟偏移导致提前/延迟删除 | 使用 server-side timestamp 或考虑 toleration |\n| annotation 缺失导致资源泄漏 | 由 workloadmanager 创建时保证 annotation 存在 |\n| 删除失败重试风暴 | controller-runtime 内置 exponential backoff |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Implementation Checklist\n\n1. **Phase 1: 搭建框架**\n   - [ ] 创建 `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go`，定义 Reconciler 结构体\n   - [ ] 创建 `cmd/agentd/main.go`，启动 manager\n   - [ ] 注册 Scheme (core + sandboxv1alpha1)\n\n2. **Phase 2: 实现 Reconcile 逻辑**\n   - [ ] 实现 annotation 解析与时间计算\n   - [ ] 实现删除逻辑与错误处理\n   - [ ] 实现 RequeueAfter 调度\n\n3. **Phase 3: 测试**\n   - [ ] 单元测试：解析成功/失败场景\n   - [ ] 单元测试：过期/未过期场景\n   - [ ] 单元测试：Get/Delete 错误处理\n\n4. **Phase 4: 部署配置**\n   - [ ] 编写 Deployment/DaemonSet manifest\n   - [ ] 配置 RBAC (Sandbox CRUD 权限)\n\n---\n\n## 7. References\n\n- AR-007: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n- `idle-cleanup/design.md`: 详细设计文档\n- `idle-cleanup/spec.md`: 需求规格\n- controller-runtime: https://pkg.go.dev/sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/defaults.go`: Annotation 常量定义\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go`: 现有 GC 实现参考"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/config_test.go":[{"range":{"start":{"line":37,"character":14},"end":{"line":37,"character":14}},"severity":3,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/go/analysis/passes/unusedwrite"},"source":"unusedwrite","message":"unused write to field WriteTimeout"},{"range":{"start":{"line":38,"character":13},"end":{"line":38,"character":13}},"severity":3,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/go/analysis/passes/unusedwrite"},"source":"unusedwrite","message":"unused write to field IdleTimeout"},{"range":{"start":{"line":39,"character":17},"end":{"line":39,"character":17}},"severity":3,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/go/analysis/passes/unusedwrite"},"source":"unusedwrite","message":"unused write to field ShutdownTimeout"},{"range":{"start":{"line":40,"character":15},"end":{"line":40,"character":15}},"severity":3,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/go/analysis/passes/unusedwrite"},"source":"unusedwrite","message":"unused write to field EnableHealthz"},{"range":{"start":{"line":41,"character":14},"end":{"line":41,"character":14}},"severity":3,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/go/analysis/passes/unusedwrite"},"source":"unusedwrite","message":"unused write to field EnableReadyz"}],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/types.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/common/types/sandbox.go":[{"range":{"start":{"line":60,"character":40},"end":{"line":60,"character":71}},"severity":4,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/go/analysis/passes/modernize#omitzero"},"source":"omitzero","message":"Omitempty has no effect on nested struct fields"}],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/cmd/picod/main.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/k8s_client.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/defaults.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/informers.go":[],"/home/dsj/b